{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 1159793, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 229189, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "每年呀", "timestamp": 1614492572, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1159806, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 229189, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "已经🈚了", "timestamp": 1614492639, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1159813, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 229189, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "事实上评上帽子能否招博士也是由学院决定的，因为名额是分配到学院的，学院再给各个研究人员。有时候你评上了帽子也不一定能带博士生。我身边就有这样的例子。不过总体来说评上了帽子以后就能招博士了。青千级别可能一年一个到两个，到杰青或者长江就一般一年两个或三个了。", "timestamp": 1614492701, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1159838, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 229189, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "soga，谢各位", "timestamp": 1614492862, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 4, "pid": 229189, "reply": 4, "tag": null, "text": "据说一个帽子（比如青千之类的）可以多招收一个博士\n那这个是仅对评上当年还是评上之后每年多一个", "timestamp": 1614492555, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1614492863, "url": "", "vote": {}}}